headline: M&T Bank Corporation Announces Fourth Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: M&T Bank Corporation ("M&T") (NYSE:MTB) will announce its fourth quarter and full-year 2025 earnings results in a press release that will be issued before the market opens on Friday, January 16, 2026.

headline: M&T Bank Stock: Is MTB Underperforming the Financial Services Sector?
summary: While M&T Bank has lagged behind the financial services sector over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook on its prospects.
